<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://jproc.ca/radiostor/titanic.html" class="external text" title="http://jproc.ca/radiostor/titanic.html" rel="nofollow">"Wireless and the Titanic"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://jproc.ca/radiostor/titanic.html" class="external free" title="http://jproc.ca/radiostor/titanic.html" rel="nofollow">http://jproc.ca/radiostor/titanic.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Wireless+and+the+Titanic&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fjproc.ca%2Fradiostor%2Ftitanic.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:RMS_Titanic"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
